# 🏠 House Price Prediction - Machine Learning Project

This project uses regression techniques to predict house prices based on various features like area, quality, and garage size.

## 📊 Dataset

- [Kaggle: House Prices - Advanced Regression Techniques](https://www.kaggle.com/c/house-prices-advanced-regression-techniques)

## ⚙️ Tools Used

- Python (Jupyter Notebook)
- Pandas, NumPy
- Matplotlib, Seaborn
- Scikit-Learn
- Streamlit (for app deployment)

## 🧠 Model

Trained a Linear Regression model on features:

- `OverallQual`
- `GrLivArea`
- `GarageCars`
- `TotalBsmtSF`

Achieved an **R² score** of ~0.80 on test data.

